    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0730c26"/><head><date from-iso="0689-12-21" key="j19730671978610" to-iso="0705-02-24">周</date>京兆廣福寺<persName key="A009243">會隱</persName>傳</head><p>
<lb ed="T" n="0730c27"/><persName key="A009243">釋會隱</persName>，不詳何許人也。精明之氣，綽有盈
<lb ed="T" n="0730c28"/>餘，處于等夷，若雞群之見鶴也。<date from-iso="0650" key="j19585081970910" to-iso="0684">天皇</date>朝慎
<lb ed="T" n="0730c29"/>選高學名德，<persName key="A009243">隱</persName>膺斯選。<date from-iso="0665-01-25" key="j19639711964354" to-iso="0666-02-12">麟德二年</date>勅北門<pb ed="T" n="0731a" xml:id="T50.2061.0731a"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0731a01"/><placeName key="CN0610102T57AA">西龍門修書所</placeName>，同與<placeName key="CN0610103T02AA">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A009244">玄則</persName>等一十人
<lb ed="T" n="0731a02"/>於一切經中略出精義玄文三十卷，號《禪林
<lb ed="T" n="0731a03"/>要鈔》，書成奏呈，勅藏祕閣。<persName key="A009243">隱</persName>亦甞預翻譯，
<lb ed="T" n="0731a04"/><persName key="A009244">玄則</persName>頗聞著述，<persName key="A002146">高宗</persName>朝斯為龍象之最焉。</p>
